<v-app class="white">

  <v-snackbar
      v-model="snackWithButtons"
      :timeout="timeout"
      bottom
      left
      class="snack"
    >
      {{ snackWithBtnText }}
      <v-spacer />
      <v-btn
        dark
        flat
        color="#00f500"
        @click.native="refreshApp"
      >
        {{ snackBtnText }}
      </v-btn>
      <v-btn
        icon
        @click="snackWithButtons = false"
      >
        <v-icon>close</v-icon>
      </v-btn>
  </v-snackbar>


  <CoreToolbar/>
  <CoreDrawer/>
  <CoreView/>
  
  <CoreFooter/>
  <BottomNav/>
</v-app>
